videos.description: Wichita State guard Austin Reaves knocks down the contested 3-pointer and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Reaves nails 3 plus the foul

videos.description: Wichita State big man Shaquille Lawson takes contact and makes a jumper to give the Shockers the lead over SMU.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Lawson powers for 3-point play

videos.description: Wichita State's Austin Reaves drops his third 3-pointer of the half.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Reaves makes SMU pay for poor defense

videos.description: SMU guard Jahmal McMurray drains an NBA-range trey to beat the buzzer before halftime.
videos.headline: SMU ends the first half on a high note

videos.description: Wichita State forward Markis McDuffie drains his third trey of the game to give him a game-high 24 points against SMU.
videos.headline: Wichita State's McDuffie continues big game with 3
